author: Cath Beedie
text:
Bottom trawling is now permanently banned in four offshore UK Marine Protected Areas (MPAs). But dozens more UK MPAs are still being plundered by industrial fishing vessels.

Politicians must go further and ban destructive fishing from ALL UK MPAs: https://t.co/QxevD0OtfZ
